    - `h_self_bnd`: per-lane `|self[k][ℓ]| ≤ 29439` (drives `sub`'s overflow bound).
    - `h_b_bnd`: per-lane `|b[k][ℓ]| ≤ 32767` (consumed by `mont_mul`'s
      legacy precondition; the impl's later `sub` then uses `|t1| ≤ 3328` from
      mont's output bound). -/
